# Smart Electrician - WordPress Theme

## 🔗 Live Demo
https://www.wpthemesdemo.com/smart-electrician/

---

## 📌 Overview
Smart Electrician is a custom-built WordPress theme designed for electricians, electrical service providers, and local service businesses.

The theme focuses on clear service presentation, lead generation, and a professional online presence.

Ideal for:
- Electricians
- Electrical contractors
- Repair & maintenance services
- Local service businesses

---

## ✨ Features
- Fully custom WordPress theme (no page builder dependency)
- Clean and professional UI design
- Fully responsive (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Service listing with clear call-to-actions
- Contact form and lead generation sections
- SEO-friendly structure
- Fast loading and performance optimized
- Cross-browser compatibility

---

